I would like to do so.

9
00:01:54,820 --> 00:01:57,660
Thank you, Your Highness.

10
00:01:59,539 --> 00:02:03,300
Congratulations, Your Highness, on your new pupil.

11
00:02:03,380 --> 00:02:05,540
Congratulations, Grand Mentor.

12
00:02:06,380 --> 00:02:08,620
I will lead the troops to the south soon.

13
00:02:09,100 --> 00:02:10,259
I'll be gone for several years.

14
00:02:10,860 --> 00:02:12,580
My entire mansion is full of warriors.

15
00:02:12,940 --> 00:02:14,940
No one will be able to take care of a young lady.

16
00:02:15,860 --> 00:02:17,940
After I win victory in the battle of Jiangshui,

17
00:02:18,540 --> 00:02:19,860
send her to the Western State.

18
00:02:21,220 --> 00:02:22,380
It's a deal.

19
00:02:22,460 --> 00:02:23,340
It's a deal.

20
00:02:33,860 --> 00:02:35,140
Uncle, please stay.

21
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,870
What does Your Majesty want from me?

22
00:02:45,900 --> 00:02:48,220
You've been guarding the territory for my father for many years.

23
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:49,380
You've had hard work.

24
00:02:51,820 --> 00:02:52,700
I'll accept this obeisance

25
00:02:53,020 --> 00:02:54,110
for the soldiers.

26
00:02:55,700 --> 00:02:56,540
Go back now.

27
00:02:56,900 --> 00:02:57,860
I'm leaving the palace.

28
00:02:59,260 --> 00:03:01,500
Won't you stay here for the night?

29
00:03:05,660 --> 00:03:06,620
This place...

30
00:03:06,780 --> 00:03:08,140
is not for me to stay.

31
00:03:08,540 --> 00:03:10,340
When will I see you again?

32
00:03:12,980 --> 00:03:13,900
The day of the funeral.

33
00:03:14,820 --> 00:03:15,700
I'll be there.

34
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:29,340
[Xuan Tombs]

35
00:04:19,899 --> 00:04:20,660
Stop.

36
00:04:28,740 --> 00:04:30,140
Today, there is no ruler or subject.

37
00:04:30,220 --> 00:04:31,300
Only the elder and the younger.

38
00:04:31,420 --> 00:04:33,420
Uncle, please hold the funeral ceremony.

39
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:34,860
I'm a prince with foreign last name.

40
00:04:34,980 --> 00:04:36,180
I'm not allowed to enter the royal tombs.

41
00:04:36,620 --> 00:04:37,659
Uncle.

42
00:04:40,900 --> 00:04:41,659
Zhao Teng.

43
00:04:42,140 --> 00:04:43,100
I'm here.

44
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:45,780
I grant my uncle the sword and the golden battle-axe.

45
00:04:45,900 --> 00:04:48,140
From now on, uncle, you don't need to report things with your title.

46
00:04:48,220 --> 00:04:49,700
You don't have to walk to the court.

47
00:04:49,820 --> 00:04:51,260
You may wear your sword in the hall.

48
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,580
Thank Your Majesty for your kindness.

49
00:05:04,170 --> 00:05:05,220
I don't need

50
00:05:05,460 --> 00:05:06,340
these extraneous things.

51
00:05:06,660 --> 00:05:07,740
Uncle.

52
00:05:09,180 --> 00:05:11,220
Your Majesty, take care.

53
00:05:30,860 --> 00:05:33,820
In the fourth year of Shunchang, the emperor passed away.

54
00:05:34,300 --> 00:05:36,460
At the age of six, the Crown Prince was crowned.

55
00:05:54,940 --> 00:05:57,220
Kneel down.

56
00:06:00,260 --> 00:06:02,580
Halloo!

57
00:06:02,900 --> 00:06:04,380
Long live the emperor!

58
00:06:04,900 --> 00:06:07,420
Halloo!

59
00:06:07,420 --> 00:06:09,100
Long live the emperor!

60
00:06:09,140 --> 00:06:12,300
Again!

61
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:14,500
Long live the emperor!

62
00:06:14,620 --> 00:06:16,780
Pay homage!

63
00:06:21,180 --> 00:06:24,740
[Xianyang Hall]

64
00:06:23,900 --> 00:06:24,740
I know

65
00:06:24,860 --> 00:06:27,260
there has always been a burden in your heart

66
00:06:27,380 --> 00:06:29,860
since the late emperor was alive, Cui.

67
00:06:32,620 --> 00:06:35,820
This is the royal decree for the engagement of the Crown Princess.

68
00:06:37,100 --> 00:06:40,020
Cui, this is a great joy.

69
00:06:40,220 --> 00:06:42,380
Cui, accept the royal decree.

70
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:46,820
When the late emperor granted the marriage,

71
00:06:47,020 --> 00:06:48,620
His Majesty was the Crown Prince

72
00:06:49,060 --> 00:06:51,380
and the young lady of Cui family would be the Crown Princess.

73
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:54,300
Now that His Majesty is the emperor,

74
00:06:54,420 --> 00:06:57,980
I think the young lady of Cui family should be the empress.

75
00:06:58,260 --> 00:06:59,700
This decree

76
00:06:59,860 --> 00:07:00,860
is wrongly made.

77
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:04,780
The late emperor made the daughter of Cui family the Crown Princess,

78
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:06,460
not the empress.

79
00:07:06,740 --> 00:07:08,820
You don't have to be so aggressive, Cui.

80
00:07:08,940 --> 00:07:11,460
His Majesty's accession to the throne is a celebration for all the country.

81
00:07:11,620 --> 00:07:14,060
How about the royal family and the Cui family

82
00:07:14,180 --> 00:07:16,060
each take a step back?

83
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:19,500
We've already made our concessions.

84
00:07:19,620 --> 00:07:21,620
What more do you want, Cui?

85
00:07:24,100 --> 00:07:25,780
I dare to ask.

86
00:07:26,060 --> 00:07:27,580
His Majesty is only six years old.

87
00:07:27,700 --> 00:07:29,060
How can there be a crown prince?

88
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:31,500
Isn't this decree

89
00:07:31,700 --> 00:07:34,620
invalid?

90
00:07:34,700 --> 00:07:35,980
Please be at ease, Cui.

91
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:37,540
The crown prince is here.

92
00:07:47,030 --> 00:07:49,580
Zixing is here to see Your Majesty.

93
00:07:49,659 --> 00:07:51,980
And Your Highness.

94
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:55,620
Get up.

95
00:07:56,700 --> 00:07:58,420
Thank you, Your Majesty.

96
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:09,260
This is the third son of Prince of Wuyan.

97
00:08:09,380 --> 00:08:10,340
Liu Zixing.

98
00:08:10,460 --> 00:08:11,140
From now on,

99
00:08:11,260 --> 00:08:12,260
he will stay long in the palace

100
00:08:12,380 --> 00:08:13,940
as His Majesty's course company.

101
00:08:14,060 --> 00:08:16,340
When he reaches twenty years old, he will be the crowned Prince.

102
00:08:16,580 --> 00:08:17,300
Cui,

103
00:08:17,420 --> 00:08:20,900
are you satisfied with this Crown Prince?

104
00:08:32,100 --> 00:08:32,820
Grand Mentor.

105
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:36,460
It's better to have this decree than without it.

106
00:08:48,860 --> 00:08:52,700
Thank you, Your Majesty.

107
00:09:08,340 --> 00:09:10,060
[De'an Hall]

108
00:09:11,980 --> 00:09:13,420
Take them all away.

109
00:09:14,020 --> 00:09:14,540
Yes.

110
00:09:19,940 --> 00:09:20,740
Be careful.

111
00:09:20,740 --> 00:09:21,300
Stop!

112
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:25,660
Stop!

113
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:26,980
Your Highness.

114
00:09:32,180 --> 00:09:35,060
The Empress Dowager Gao family has been executed.

115
00:09:39,140 --> 00:09:43,980
[Years later]

116
00:09:51,980 --> 00:09:53,540
That's a big family.

117
00:09:54,100 --> 00:09:55,580
The Cui family is the leader

118
00:09:55,660 --> 00:09:56,660
of all the clans north of the river.

119
00:09:56,780 --> 00:09:57,940
Our dynasty's title was

120
00:09:58,060 --> 00:09:58,620
decided

121
00:09:58,700 --> 00:09:59,620
after Cui

122
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:00,780
proposed it to the emperor at that time.

123
00:10:02,060 --> 00:10:03,380
That's powerful.

124
00:10:03,380 --> 00:10:04,860
That's right.

125
00:10:09,620 --> 00:10:10,380
Stop the carriage.

126
00:10:35,580 --> 00:10:36,540
You didn't have your lunch?

127
00:10:38,620 --> 00:10:42,060
[Cui Feng]

128
00:10:39,020 --> 00:10:40,860
He's the one who gave up his royal last name

129
00:10:40,980 --> 00:10:42,420
to lead troops and protect the country.

130
00:10:42,620 --> 00:10:43,500
Don't you want to see him

131
00:10:43,660 --> 00:10:45,020
by this?

132
00:10:46,100 --> 00:10:47,620
You already told me.

133
00:10:47,820 --> 00:10:49,180
He has fought all over the country as a teen

134
00:10:49,300 --> 00:10:50,780
and never lost a battle.

135
00:10:50,900 --> 00:10:51,780
Don't you feel curious

136
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:53,500
about such a man?

137
00:10:53,900 --> 00:10:55,540
You also told me.

138
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:57,260
He had many other

139
00:10:57,340 --> 00:10:58,500
famous battles.

140
00:10:58,580 --> 00:10:59,820
Flooding Jiang State.

141
00:10:59,940 --> 00:11:01,020
The fierce battle of Shuo State.

142
00:11:01,140 --> 00:11:02,260
Six battles in Dai State.

143
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:04,380
These are all great battles that can be written in the military books

144
00:11:04,500 --> 00:11:06,020
and remembered for generations to come.

145
00:11:08,700 --> 00:11:09,620
All right.

146
00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:11,220
I've said all of them.

147
00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:13,860
You don't want to leave the family.

148
00:11:13,940 --> 00:11:15,060
As your elder brother, I understand.

149
00:11:15,220 --> 00:11:16,980
So I stay and join the army

150
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:18,500
to accompany you.

151
00:11:19,140 --> 00:11:20,740
Father has already agreed.

152
00:11:21,140 --> 00:11:23,060
I don't have to inherit the family business anyway.

153
00:11:23,220 --> 00:11:23,700
If I can stay

154
00:11:23,820 --> 00:11:25,540
under the command of Jr. Prince of Nanchen to toughen myself,

155
00:11:25,700 --> 00:11:28,020
I'm sure there's no reason for Father to disagree.

156
00:11:29,340 --> 00:11:30,260
Now you feel happy?

157
00:11:32,740 --> 00:11:33,900
Simple girl.

158
00:11:39,620 --> 00:11:44,620
[Western State]

159
00:11:54,580 --> 00:11:56,860
[Western State]

160
00:12:05,100 --> 00:12:07,100
I'm Zhou Tianxing. Greetings to you two.

161
00:12:08,260 --> 00:12:09,540
Cui Shou from the Cui family.

162
00:12:09,820 --> 00:12:10,740
This is the young lord.

163
00:12:12,700 --> 00:12:13,700
We've won a great victory at the border.

164
00:12:13,900 --> 00:12:15,340
Master has returned to the city.

165
00:12:15,460 --> 00:12:16,580
He will arrive tomorrow.

166
00:12:16,900 --> 00:12:17,580
All distinguished guests,

167
00:12:17,700 --> 00:12:18,900
please follow me back to the royal mansion.

168
00:12:19,100 --> 00:12:20,140
The clan chief has orders

169
00:12:20,260 --> 00:12:20,860
that we should all stay at the post

170
00:12:20,980 --> 00:12:22,260
before paying respect to the master.

171
00:12:22,620 --> 00:12:24,020
We won't need to bother you, General Zhou.

172
00:12:24,260 --> 00:12:24,900
But

173
00:12:24,900 --> 00:12:26,620
Master ordered this in person.

174
00:12:26,740 --> 00:12:27,940
It's just a couple of days.

175
00:12:28,100 --> 00:12:28,700
General Zhou.

176
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:30,540
Let's go to the posthouse first.

177
00:12:31,300 --> 00:12:33,060
All right, please.

178
00:12:33,460 --> 00:12:33,780
Let's go.

179
00:12:34,100 --> 00:12:34,940
Let's go.

180
00:12:34,660 --> 00:12:37,700
[Western State]

181
00:12:42,540 --> 00:12:46,580
[Western State]

182
00:12:46,580 --> 00:12:52,860
[Qing'an Post]

183
00:12:52,140 --> 00:12:52,860
General Zhou.

184
00:12:54,100 --> 00:12:55,340
When will His Highness return?

185
00:12:55,460 --> 00:12:56,700
He'll be here before dawn for sure.

186
00:12:57,180 --> 00:12:57,860
Master likes to review the royal military parade the most

187
00:12:57,980 --> 00:12:59,700
when the sun rises in the east.

188
00:12:59,820 --> 00:13:00,620
This has been his habit

189
00:13:00,740 --> 00:13:01,700
for many years.

190
00:13:02,380 --> 00:13:03,940
Shall I have a chance to see it?

191
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:07,700
You are not a member of the royal mansion.

192
00:13:07,820 --> 00:13:09,220
I'd like to take my sister to see it.

193
00:13:09,340 --> 00:13:10,420
We won't disturb them.

194
00:13:10,540 --> 00:13:12,140
We'll just watch from the city from afar.

195
00:13:16,380 --> 00:13:17,100
At dawn,

196
00:13:17,500 --> 00:13:18,140
take this

197
00:13:18,300 --> 00:13:20,380
[Nanchen]

198
00:13:18,540 --> 00:13:19,740
and tell the soldiers who are guarding the city

199
00:13:19,860 --> 00:13:20,740
I'm the one who takes you there.

200
00:13:22,340 --> 00:13:23,380
Thank you, General Zhou.

201
00:13:23,780 --> 00:13:25,100
I'll take my leave now.

202
00:13:25,380 --> 00:13:26,300
Take care, General.

203
00:13:26,460 --> 00:13:35,660
[Qing'an Post]

204
00:13:40,020 --> 00:13:40,580
Auntie.

205
00:13:51,180 --> 00:13:52,500
Don't fall sound asleep at night.

206
00:13:52,940 --> 00:13:53,980
When you hear the bamboo whistle,

207
00:13:54,060 --> 00:13:55,020
come out and find me.

208
00:13:56,420 --> 00:13:57,700
I'll take you to see the master.

209
00:14:36,380 --> 00:14:36,860
Let's go.

210
00:14:41,340 --> 00:14:42,620
How do you feel? Are you sleepy?

211
00:14:44,900 --> 00:14:47,980
[Daxing Gate]

212
00:14:47,300 --> 00:14:48,020
Who is it?

213
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:51,060
Don't be afraid.

214
00:14:52,940 --> 00:14:54,180
This is General Zhou's token.

215
00:14:54,300 --> 00:14:55,460
He allows us to go up to the city tower

216
00:14:55,580 --> 00:14:57,140
to watch the sunrise parade of the army.

217
00:14:58,340 --> 00:14:59,780
If you don't trust us,

218
00:14:59,900 --> 00:15:01,140
you can keep watch on us.

219
00:15:03,340 --> 00:15:03,740
Please.

220
00:15:03,900 --> 00:15:04,500
Thank you.

221
00:15:08,940 --> 00:15:11,940
[Western State]

222
00:15:35,660 --> 00:15:37,060
The one who will step on that platform

223
00:15:37,180 --> 00:15:38,580
is your future master.

224
00:15:43,060 --> 00:15:43,820
He's coming!

225
00:15:43,980 --> 00:15:44,660
He's there!

