00:16:38,900 --> 00:16:42,580
Witnessed by the world, loyally stick to the righteousness.

235
00:16:40,440 --> 00:16:44,360
♫I'm suffering with you♫

236
00:16:42,740 --> 00:16:46,220
Witnessed by the world, loyally stick to the righteousness.

237
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:48,160
♫Suffered so much from this sea of pain♫

238
00:16:51,460 --> 00:16:55,080
♫I can leap down for you♫

