241
00:16:59,140 --> 00:17:01,390
♫The rivers and mountains, the ostentatious world♫

242
00:16:59,220 --> 00:17:02,940
The smoke of wolf's dung rises, the yellow sand fills the sky.

243
00:17:01,680 --> 00:17:06,869
♫Swords and horses, leave the dust of this world behind♫

